        Bugs
        ~~~~
        
        No bugs, of course. ;-)
        But if you've found one or have an idea how to improve rcssmin, feel free
        to send a pull request on `github <https://github.com/ndparker/rcssmin>`_
        or send a mail to <rcssmin-bugs@perlig.de>.
        
        
